OL,3,CHMRC 'degrading its own services as a
OL,4,Cmatter of policy'
OL,6,FHM Revenue and Customs (HMRC) has been
OL,7,Faccused by a public spending watchdog
OL,8,Fof degrading its own services "as a
OL,9,Fmatter of policy" and damaging public
OL,10,Fconfidence in the tax system.
OL,12,FConcerns about a deteriorating
OL,13,Fservice, uncollectable debt and a
OL,14,Freduction in prosecutions were
OL,15,Fhighlighted by the Public Accounts
OL,16,FCommittee (PAC).
OL,18,FThe PAC said it is concerned that the
OL,19,Ftax authority has sought to degrade
OL,20,Fits telephone service to drive
OL,21,Ftaxpayers to digital channels.
OL,26,@pD@_OUqD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
