OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F303A1737507298
OL,3,CHMRC 'degrading its own services as a
OL,4,Cmatter of policy'
OL,6,FBut HMRC hit back strongly, with Jim
OL,7,FHarra, First Permanent Secretary and
OL,8,Fchief executive of the revenue body
OL,9,Fdescribing the committee's claims
OL,10,Faround HMRC's customer service as
OL,11,F"completely baseless".
OL,13,FMr Harra said: "The committee's claims
OL,14,Fabout our customer service are
OL,15,Fcompletely baseless. In reality, we've
OL,16,Fmade huge improvements to our service
OL,17,Fstandards, with call wait times down
OL,18,Fby 17 minutes since April last year.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@UO]uD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
