OL,3,CHMRC 'degrading its own services as a
OL,4,Cmatter of policy'
OL,6,FHMRC said its latest figures show call
OL,7,Fwait times have fallen to around 11
OL,8,Fminutes, compared with around 28
OL,9,Fminutes in April 2024.
OL,11,FBut the PAC report said HMRC should
OL,12,Ftake responsibility for how it has
OL,13,Ffailed its customers, act more boldly
OL,14,Fto tackle tax system abuse, including
OL,15,Finvestigating more cases of
OL,16,Fcriminality, and pursue debts and
OL,17,Fwealth hidden offshore more
OL,18,Feffectively.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
