OL,3,CHMRC 'degrading its own services as a
OL,4,Cmatter of policy'
OL,6,FThe watchdog said evidence to its
OL,7,Finquiry shows trust in the system is
OL,8,Feroding.
OL,10,FHMRC has said that encouraging
OL,11,Fcustomers to go digital frees up
OL,12,Fphonelines for vulnerable people and
OL,13,Fmore complex cases.
OL,15,FBut the PAC report warned that phone
OL,16,Faccess has been restricted before
OL,17,Fdigital services are ready.
OL,19,FThe report also urged HMRC to set out
OL,20,Fa plan for how it will collect older
OL,21,Fdebts before they become uncollectable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
