OL,3,CHMRC 'degrading its own services as a
OL,4,Cmatter of policy'
OL,6,FIn 2023-24, #5 billion in debts were
OL,7,Fwritten off as uncollectable, up from
OL,8,F#3.2 billion in 2022-23, with a risk
OL,9,Fthis could apply to an estimated 45%
OL,10,Fof debt owed to the public purse, the
OL,11,FPAC said.
OL,13,FHMRC reported total revenues of #843.4
OL,14,Fbillion for 2023-24, the highest on
OL,15,Frecord, representing a 3.6% increase
OL,16,Fon 2022-23.
OL,18,FThe report also said the tax authority
OL,19,Fshould be bolder in identifying and
OL,20,Ftackling abuse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
