CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F303A1737507298
OL,3,CHMRC 'degrading its own services as a
OL,4,Cmatter of policy'
OL,6,F"Worse, it seems to be degrading its
OL,7,Fown services as a matter of policy.
OL,8,FHMRC is an organisation in defensive
OL,9,Fmode, and needs bold and ambitious
OL,10,Fleadership to begin to chart its
OL,11,Frecovery.
OL,13,F"There is some hope in our report.
OL,14,FHMRC has now secured more funds to
OL,15,Fallow it to pursue what's owed to it,
OL,16,Fand has a welcome new goal to reduce
OL,17,Fthe gap in unpaid tax.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
