OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F303A1737507298
OL,3,CHMRC 'degrading its own services as a
OL,4,Cmatter of policy'
OL,6,F"We would urge it to use its new
OL,7,Fresources not to just go after low-
OL,8,Fhanging fruit, but to do more to
OL,9,Frecover older debts lest they become
OL,10,Funcollectable, as well as to better
OL,11,Funderstand what more may be hidden
OL,12,Foffshore.
OL,14,F"Further, if it is serious in its
OL,15,Fplans to reduce its prosecutions, it
OL,16,Fshould also explain what the best
OL,17,Fmeans of deterring criminal tax
OL,18,Fevaders may be."
OL,20,FThe report said HMRC does not consider
OL,21,Fcustomers' needs enough.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@PO]
