OL,3,CHMRC 'degrading its own services as a
OL,4,Cmatter of policy'
OL,6,FIn 2023-24, performance reached an all-
OL,7,Ftime low, with 66.4% of customers'
OL,8,Fattempts to speak to an adviser
OL,9,Fanswered, against a target of 85%, and
OL,10,Faverage call waiting times exceeding
OL,11,F23 minutes.
OL,13,FThe PAC said it had received written
OL,14,Fsubmissions from organisations
OL,15,Frepresenting taxpayers and agents
OL,16,Fsaying continual failings in customer
OL,17,Fservice had eroded trust in HMRC.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
