OL,3,CHMRC 'degrading its own services as a
OL,4,Cmatter of policy'
OL,6,FIn the first 11 months of 2023-24,
OL,7,FHMRC cut off nearly 44,000 customers
OL,8,Fwho had been waiting 70 minutes to
OL,9,Fspeak to an adviser.
OL,11,FIt did not warn customers their call
OL,12,Fwould be cut off, or call them back,
OL,13,Fthe PAC said.
OL,15,FHMRC should reinstate a call waiting
OL,16,Ftime target as a key performance
OL,17,Fmeasure and must ensure it gives
OL,18,Fcustomers accurate wait estimates in
OL,19,Freal time, does not cut people off
OL,20,Fwithout warning, and offers a callback
OL,21,Fservice, the watchdog recommended.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
