OL,3,CHMRC 'degrading its own services as a
OL,4,Cmatter of policy'
OL,6,FThe tax authority has been working to
OL,7,Fbecome a "digital-first" organisation
OL,8,Fsince 2010, but telephone demand has
OL,9,Fremained high, with 37 million calls
OL,10,Fin 2023-24, the PAC said.
OL,12,FHMRC has said it has not had enough
OL,13,Fresources to deal with all the contact
OL,14,Fit has been receiving with, for
OL,15,Fexample, three million more income
OL,16,Ftaxpayers in the past two years as a
OL,17,Fresult of freezing tax thresholds.
OL,19,FIn May 2024, HMRC received #51 million
OL,20,Fin additional funding to bring
OL,21,Fcustomer service to target levels.
OL,26,@oD@JOUoD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
