OL,3,CHMRC 'degrading its own services as a
OL,4,Cmatter of policy'
OL,6,FBut the PAC said it is concerned that
OL,7,Fperformance will deteriorate again.
OL,9,FIt recommended that the tax body
OL,10,Fshould establish "guard rails",
OL,11,Fmeaning that when service levels fall
OL,12,Fmore than five percentage points below
OL,13,Ftarget levels, it should trigger a
OL,14,Fcorrective response with additional
OL,15,Fresources deployed if needed, the PAC
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,26,@rD@ROUrD@^O]
