OL,3,CHMRC 'degrading its own services as a
OL,4,Cmatter of policy'
OL,6,FHMRC should also ensure it meets a
OL,7,Fminimum level of service for all
OL,8,Fcustomers, including the seven million
OL,9,Fcustomers HMRC estimates cannot use
OL,10,Fdigital services, the PAC said.
OL,12,FIn 2022-23, HMRC received 22 million
OL,13,Fitems of correspondence, with around
OL,14,F70% by post.
OL,16,FIn the past, the agency has faced
OL,17,Flarge backlogs in processing
OL,18,Fcorrespondence, clearing only 45.5%
OL,19,Fwithin 15 working days of receipt in
OL,20,F2021-22, the PAC said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
