OL,3,CHMRC 'degrading its own services as a
OL,4,Cmatter of policy'
OL,6,FIn spring 2025, HMRC plans to publish
OL,7,Fa plan for further development of its
OL,8,Fdigital services.
OL,10,FThe PAC said that as part of its
OL,11,Fdigital road map, HMRC should
OL,12,Fprioritise introducing systems for
OL,13,Fcustomers to submit files and send
OL,14,Fsecure messages electronically.
OL,16,FThe committee also raised concerns
OL,17,Fover HMRC's goal to reduce the tax gap
OL,18,F` the gap between the tax it estimates
OL,19,Fis owed and the tax collected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
