OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F303A1737507298
OL,3,CHMRC 'degrading its own services as a
OL,4,Cmatter of policy'
OL,6,FHMRC can use civil processes to
OL,7,Fsanction non-compliance, but its use
OL,8,Fof criminal investigation and
OL,9,Fprosecution is decreasing, with 344
OL,10,Fcriminal prosecutions in 2023-24, down
OL,11,Ffrom 691 in 2019-20, with HMRC
OL,12,Ffocusing on the most serious and high-
OL,13,Fvalue cases, the PAC said.
OL,15,FThe tax body should obtain an estimate
OL,16,Fthat is as accurate as possible of the
OL,17,Foffshore tax gap and develop a
OL,18,Fstrategy to reduce it, the report said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/16
